{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ezra's Legacy is an action packed 2d platformer inspired in classics from the 80s and 90s gaming era, with 8-bit aesthetics, great soundtrack and awesome gameplay. You play as Ruby, a young apprentice witch whose apprenticeship is abruptly interrupted by having her aunt and master Amber kidnapped by the fearsome Dark Council.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With still much to learn but already a lot of confidence, Ruby embarks on a journey across the land to search for her master and, unknowingly, uncover the Council plot regarding the legendary witch, Ezra, and her legacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you love fun and simple games, but with challenging difficulty, polished retro stile graphics, highly hummable chiptune music and simple but engaging mechanics, then Ezra's Legacy is just for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Enjoy Ezra's legacy unique art stile, where art, music, story and gameplay work together to bring you a harmonious and wonderful gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Challenge your platforming skills as you pursue and defeat each member of the Dark Council.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Enter &quot;in the zone&quot; while listening to each of the highly memorable and hummable tunes from the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Equip Ruby with the gems recovered from each Council member, granting you either an attack spell or a passive ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore an immersive game map where secrets can be hidden in any corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade ruby with lost Ezra artifacts, granting her new gameplay abilities.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738696016","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic