ach of the highly memorable and hummable tunes from the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Equip Ruby with the gems recovered from each Council member, granting you either an attack spell or a passive ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore an immersive game map where secrets can be hidden in any corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade ruby with lost Ezra artifacts, granting her new gameplay abilities.</p></li></ul>","developers":["gnumaru"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454130/header.jpg?t=1738696016","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04 or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core 2 Duo 2.0 ghz or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 2nd Generation Intel Core HD Graphics (2000/3000), 512MB<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 250 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Requires an OpenGL 3 capable graphics driver</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Compatible up to 10.15.17 Catalina<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core 2 Duo 2.0 ghz or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 2nd Generation Intel Core HD Graphics (2000/3000), 512MB<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 250 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Requires an OpenGL 3 capable graphics driver</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256961473,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256961473/movie480.mp4?t=1690979217","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic